									  Gaskets					
 
 
 
 
 
 




Gaskets












 

High Quality OEM Gaskets for Commercial Refrigeration Equipment.
Our Gaskets are made using the same material, machines and processes of many OEM gaskets. In some case we are the supplier to some OEM’s!
 
We all realize that a cracked, loose or missing door gasket is bad for any refrigerator. Brittle and leaking seals cause refrigerator temperatures to be too warm resulting in spoiled food, high energy use and heavy frost buildup.
A-Cent Tech partners with a custom manufacturer of refrigeration gaskets. Specializing in providing high quality gaskets that meet or beat OEM specs at a fraction of the cost we are the premier supplier of these custom gaskets.

Any size or profile manufactured to order
Food grade quality NSF 5 1 compound
Lead and Cadmium free
Low temperature formula
Formulated compounds to retard mold and mildew growth
Walk in cooler gaskets and strip curtains are also available
Shipped typically 2-3 days from receipt of order



 
 
 





