									  Product Graphics					
 
 
 
 
 
 




Product Graphics
Graphic Messages
Let us raise your company profile, advertise a particular product or simply convey information.
Many companies over recent years have seen and taken advantage of what may be considered dead space on a night blind when it is pulled down. While the main function of the blind is to save energy many retailers have used the blind fabric for advertising when they need to close off specific refrigerated cases.
The blinds can be used to close off alcohol areas while at the same time using the space for corporate branding and to advertise or promote products.
Whatever your requirement we can print any image from single to full color on part or all over your screen.
Your imagination is the only limitation.
This slideshow requires JavaScript.
 
 
 





