Lucent

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the company from 1996 to 2006. For the company following its acquisition by Alcatel SA in 2006, see Alcatel-Lucent.

Lucent Technologies, Inc.





